page.title: 04Natural History
page.content: The area has a mixture of farmland with hedgerows and woodland.The plants insects animals and birds seen there were as follows: {Trees;}Oak,Sycamore,Ash,Chestnut,Yew, Beech,Silver birch,Hawthorn, Holly,Willow,Pine. {Wild Plants;}Nettle,Thistle,Ragwort, Fern,Clover,Dock,Cow Parsley, Shepherds Purse,Hogweed,Daisy. {Insects;}Butterfly,Bee,Wasp,Ladybird, Housefly,Gnat,Spider. {Animals;}Roe deer,Rabbit,Grey squirrel Hedgehog,Mouse,Weasel,Frog,Fox. {Birds;}Crow,Magpie,Jay,Pigeon,Pheasant Woodpecker(heard),Cuckoo(heard) Blackbird,Thrush,Robin,Sparrow, Blue Tit,and most other common garden birds.
